ez – bengurion  dinur – aran – eban – aran – allon – yadlin – hammer – navon – hammer – aloni – rabin  rubinstein – hammer – levy – sarid – barak – livnat – sheetrit  tamir – saar – piron – bennett – v t e foreign affairs ministers of israel sharett – meir – eban – allon – dayan – shamir – peres – arens – levy – peres – barak – levy – sharon – levy – benami – peres – netanyahu – shalom – livni – lieberman – netanyahu – lieberman – netanyahu – v t e aliyah and integration ministers of israel shapira – allon – peres – peled – rosen – levy – abuhatzira – uzan – tzur – peretz – tzaban – edelstein – barak  tamir – sharon – livni – boim – edri – aflalo – landver – elkin – landver – v t e ministers of the economy bernstein – kaplan – geri – yosef – bernstein – naftali  sapir – zadok – sherf – sapir – sapir – barlev – hurvitz – patt – sharon – nissim – harish – sharansky – ran cohen – barak – itzik – sharon – olmert – yishai – beneliezer – simhon – bennett – deri  netanyahu  kahlon – eli cohen – v t e interior ministers of israel gruenbaum – shapira – rokach – shapira  baryehuda – shapira – meir  burg – hillel  burg – hillel  burg – peres  peretz – shamir – deri – rabin  deri  rabin – baram  libai  barak  ramon – suissa – sharansky – ramon – yishai – sharon  yishai – poraz – pinespaz  sharon – baron – sheetrit – yishai – saar – erdan – shalom  netanyahu – deri – v t e science technology and space ministers of israel neeman – patt – weizman – neeman – rubinstein  sheetrit – aloni – begin – netanyahu – eitan – shalom – barak  vilnai – sandberg – shalgi  brailovsky  vilnai  baron  pinespaz  tamir – majadele – hershkowitz – peri – danon  akunis  v t e tourism ministers of israel govrin – kol – patt  sharir – patt – baram – katsav – barak  lipkinshahak – zeevi  elon – levy – elon – ezra – hirschson – herzog – aharonovich – avraham – misezhnikov – landau – levin – authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  bnf cb data nkc js retrieved from httpsenwiki