rotect the borders and police the trouble spots within the country today the program examines the governmental policy of compulsory military service and the details of presentday life in the field with the idf the journey to goldas balcony visual  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide documentary on william gibsons stage play goldas balcony based on the life of israeli prime minister golda meir which ran in new york during  includes excerpts from interviews with gibson performer tovah feldshuh who played meir and other members of the plays creative team meirs life and career are examined and several of her colleagues are also interviewed persona non grata by oliver stone visual  editions published in  in german and english and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide indiqué sur la jaquette   mars  israéliens et palestiniens sont en guerre la diplomatie est au point mort la violence atteint son paroxysme a la recherche dexplications et de perspectives le réalisateur oliver stone et son équipe de documentaristes européens se rendent au coeur du conflit  jérusalem tel aviv mais aussi ramallah capitale de lautorité palestinienne my country my life  fighting for israel searching for peace by ehud barak book  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide la sexagénaire jeunesse disraël book  editions published in  in french and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide nous attendrons quʹisraël atteigne lʹâge biblique de cent vingt ans pour nous lancer dans une impossible totalisation a la michemin ou la micourse dʹun déjà éblouissant parcours de vie et de survie nous proposons aux lecteurs quelque chose de plus original et de plus rare non pas un tome celuici mais deux tomes le prochain plus volumineux qui verra le jour dans deux mois ces textes à la fois compréhensifs et critiques nous permettent de pénétrer in medias res dans la réalité israélienne contemporaine